<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Data & AI Learning Roadmap Tracker</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syne:wght@400;600;700;800&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@300;400;500&family=Outfit:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --bg: #07080f;
  --surface: #0d0e1a;
  --card: #111220;
  --card2: #161727;
  --border: #1e2035;
  --border2: #252640;
  --c1: #4fffb0;
  --c2: #ff6b6b;
  --c3: #ffd166;
  --c4: #4fc3f7;
  --c5: #c084fc;
  --text: #e2e4f0;
  --muted: #555878;
  --muted2: #8890b0;
  --success: #4fffb0;
}
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth;}
body{
  background:var(--bg);
  color:var(--text);
  font-family:'Outfit',sans-serif;
  min-height:100vh;
  overflow-x:hidden;
}
body::before{
  content:'';
  position:fixed;inset:0;
  background:radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 50% at 50% -10%, rgba(79,255,176,0.04) 0%, transparent 60%),
             radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 40% at 90% 90%, rgba(79,195,247,0.03) 0%, transparent 50%);
  pointer-events:none;z-index:0;
}

/* ─── LAYOUT ─── */
.app{display:flex;min-height:100vh;position:relative;z-index:1;}

/* ─── SIDEBAR ─── */
.sidebar{
width:260px;flex-shrink:0;
background:var(–surface);
border-right:1px solid var(–border);
position:sticky;top:0;height:100vh;
overflow-y:auto;
padding:28px 0 40px;
display:flex;flex-direction:column;
scrollbar-width:thin;scrollbar-color:var(–border2) transparent;
}
.sidebar-logo{
padding:0 22px 24px;
border-bottom:1px solid var(–border);
margin-bottom:20px;
}
.sidebar-logo .logo-tag{
font-family:‘JetBrains Mono’,monospace;
font-size:9px;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;
color:var(–c1);margin-bottom:8px;
}
.sidebar-logo h2{
font-family:‘Syne’,sans-serif;
font-size:17px;font-weight:800;
line-height:1.2;
}

/* overall progress in sidebar */
.sidebar-progress{
padding:0 22px 20px;
border-bottom:1px solid var(–border);
margin-bottom:16px;
}
.sp-label{
font-family:‘JetBrains Mono’,monospace;
font-size:9px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;
color:var(–muted2);margin-bottom:8px;
display:flex;justify-content:space-between;
}
.sp-bar-bg{
height:5px;background:var(–border2);
border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden;
}
.sp-bar-fill{
height:100%;border-radius:10px;
background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(–c1),var(–c4));
transition:width 0.6s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1);
}
.sp-count{
margin-top:6px;
font-size:11px;color:var(–muted2);
font-family:‘JetBrains Mono’,monospace;
}

/* nav items */
.nav-phase{padding:0 22px;margin-bottom:6px;}
.nav-phase-label{
font-family:‘JetBrains Mono’,monospace;
font-size:9px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;
color:var(–muted);margin-bottom:4px;padding:4px 0;
}
.nav-week{
display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;
padding:8px 10px;border-radius:6px;
cursor:pointer;
text-decoration:none;color:var(–muted2);
font-size:13px;font-weight:500;
transition:all 0.15s;
position:relative;
}
.nav-week:hover{background:var(–card);color:var(–text);}
.nav-week.active{background:var(–card2);color:var(–text);}
.nav-week .nw-dot{
width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%;
flex-shrink:0;
background:var(–border2);
transition:background 0.2s;
}
.nav-week.done .nw-dot{background:var(–c1);}
.nav-week .nw-pct{
margin-left:auto;
font-family:‘JetBrains Mono’,monospace;
font-size:10px;color:var(–muted);
}

/* ─── MAIN ─── */
.main{flex:1;padding:40px 32px 80px;max-width:860px;}

/* hero */
.hero{
margin-bottom:48px;
animation:fadeUp 0.7s ease both;
}
.hero-eyebrow{
font-family:‘JetBrains Mono’,monospace;
font-size:10px;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;
color:var(–c1);margin-bottom:14px;
}
.hero h1{
font-family:‘Syne’,sans-serif;
font-size:clamp(28px,4vw,48px);
font-weight:800;line-height:1.1;
letter-spacing:-1.5px;margin-bottom:12px;
}
.hero h1 em{
font-style:normal;
background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(–c1) 0%,var(–c4) 100%);
-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;
background-clip:text;
}
.hero p{color:var(–muted2);font-size:15px;font-weight:300;line-height:1.7;max-width:580px;}

/* stat pills */
.stats-bar{
display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:10px;
margin-bottom:48px;
animation:fadeUp 0.7s 0.1s ease both;
}
.stat-pill{
background:var(–card);border:1px solid var(–border2);
border-radius:100px;padding:8px 18px;
display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;
}
.stat-pill .pn{
font-family:‘Syne’,sans-serif;
font-size:18px;font-weight:800;
}
.stat-pill .pl{font-size:12px;color:var(–muted2);font-weight:300;}
.stat-pill:nth-child(1) .pn{color:var(–c1);}
.stat-pill:nth-child(2) .pn{color:var(–c2);}
.stat-pill:nth-child(3) .pn{color:var(–c3);}
.stat-pill:nth-child(4) .pn{color:var(–c4);}

/* ─── PHASE SECTION ─── */
.phase-section{margin-bottom:56px;animation:fadeUp 0.6s ease both;}
.phase-header{
display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;
margin-bottom:24px;
padding-bottom:16px;
border-bottom:1px solid var(–border);
}
.ph-icon{
width:38px;height:38px;border-radius:8px;
display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
font-size:18px;flex-shrink:0;
}
.ph-title{
font-family:‘Syne’,sans-serif;
font-size:20px;font-weight:800;
}
.ph-sub{font-size:12px;color:var(–muted2);font-weight:300;margin-top:2px;}
.ph-weeks-badge{
margin-left:auto;
font-family:‘JetBrains Mono’,monospace;
font-size:10px;letter-spacing:1px;
padding:4px 12px;border-radius:4px;
white-space:nowrap;
}

/* ─── WEEK BLOCK ─── */
.week-block{
margin-bottom:32px;
background:var(–card);
border:1px solid var(–border);
border-radius:12px;
overflow:hidden;
}
.week-header{
display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;
padding:16px 20px;
cursor:pointer;
user-select:none;
transition:background 0.15s;
}
.week-header:hover{background:var(–card2);}
.wh-badge{
font-family:‘JetBrains Mono’,monospace;
font-size:10px;letter-spacing:1.5px;
padding:3px 10px;border-radius:3px;
white-space:nowrap;
}
.wh-title{
font-family:‘Syne’,sans-serif;
font-size:15px;font-weight:700;
flex:1;
}
.wh-progress{
display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;
}
.wh-prog-bar{
width:80px;height:4px;
background:var(–border2);border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden;
}
.wh-prog-fill{
height:100%;border-radius:10px;
transition:width 0.5s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1);
}
.wh-pct{
font-family:‘JetBrains Mono’,monospace;
font-size:11px;color:var(–muted2);
min-width:32px;text-align:right;
}
.wh-chevron{
color:var(–muted);font-size:12px;
transition:transform 0.25s;
}
.week-block.open .wh-chevron{transform:rotate(90deg);}

/* week body */
.week-body{
display:block;
padding:0 20px 20px;
border-top:1px solid var(–border);
}
.week-block.closed .week-body{display:none;}
.week-block.open .week-body{display:block;}

/* day section */
.day-section{
margin-top:20px;
padding:18px;
background:var(–surface);
border:1px solid var(–border);
border-radius:8px;
}
.day-label{
font-family:‘JetBrains Mono’,monospace;
font-size:10px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;
margin-bottom:14px;
display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;
}
.day-label::after{
content:’’;flex:1;height:1px;background:var(–border2);
}

/* task item */
.task-item{
display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:12px;
padding:10px 12px;border-radius:6px;
margin-bottom:4px;
transition:background 0.12s;
cursor:pointer;
}
.task-item:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03);}
.task-item input[type=checkbox]{
display:none;
}
.task-cb{
width:20px;height:20px;flex-shrink:0;
border-radius:5px;border:1.5px solid var(–border2);
display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
transition:all 0.15s;margin-top:1px;
background:transparent;
}
.task-item.checked .task-cb{
border-color:var(–c1);
background:rgba(79,255,176,0.12);
}
.task-cb-check{
font-size:11px;color:var(–c1);
opacity:0;transform:scale(0.5);
transition:all 0.15s;
}
.task-item.checked .task-cb-check{opacity:1;transform:scale(1);}
.task-text{
font-size:13.5px;font-weight:400;
line-height:1.5;color:var(–muted2);
transition:color 0.15s;
}
.task-item.checked .task-text{
color:var(–muted);
text-decoration:line-through;
text-decoration-color:var(–border2);
}
.task-label{
font-family:‘JetBrains Mono’,monospace;
font-size:10px;
padding:2px 7px;border-radius:3px;
margin-left:auto;flex-shrink:0;
align-self:center;
}

/* ─── SUMMARY BOX ─── */
.summary-section{
margin-top:24px;
border:1px solid var(–border2);
border-radius:8px;
overflow:hidden;
}
.summary-header{
padding:12px 16px;
display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;
font-family:‘JetBrains Mono’,monospace;
font-size:11px;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase;
font-weight:500;
}
.summary-lock{font-size:13px;}
.summary-required{
margin-left:auto;
font-size:9px;letter-spacing:1px;
padding:2px 8px;border-radius:3px;
background:rgba(255,107,107,0.1);
color:var(–c2);border:1px solid rgba(255,107,107,0.2);
}
.summary-unlocked .summary-required{
background:rgba(79,255,176,0.1);
color:var(–c1);border-color:rgba(79,255,176,0.2);
}
.summary-body{padding:0 16px 16px;}
.summary-locked-msg{
display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;
padding:14px;margin-bottom:0;
background:rgba(255,107,107,0.05);
border-radius:6px;
font-size:13px;color:var(–muted2);
font-weight:300;
}
.summary-locked-msg span{font-size:18px;}
.summary-textarea-wrap{display:none;}
.summary-unlocked .summary-locked-msg{display:none;}
.summary-unlocked .summary-textarea-wrap{display:block;}
.summary-prompt{
font-size:12.5px;color:var(–muted2);
margin-bottom:10px;line-height:1.6;
font-weight:300;
}
.summary-prompt strong{color:var(–text);font-weight:500;}
textarea.summary-input{
width:100%;
min-height:110px;
background:var(–bg);
border:1.5px solid var(–border2);
border-radius:6px;
color:var(–text);
font-family:‘Outfit’,sans-serif;
font-size:13.5px;
font-weight:300;
line-height:1.6;
padding:12px 14px;
resize:vertical;
transition:border-color 0.2s;
outline:none;
}
textarea.summary-input:focus{border-color:var(–c1);}
textarea.summary-input::placeholder{color:var(–muted);}
.summary-save-btn{
margin-top:10px;
padding:9px 20px;
border-radius:6px;
border:none;cursor:pointer;
font-family:‘Syne’,sans-serif;
font-size:13px;font-weight:700;
letter-spacing:0.5px;
transition:all 0.15s;
}
.summary-save-btn:disabled{opacity:0.3;cursor:not-allowed;}
.summary-saved-note{
display:none;
font-family:‘JetBrains Mono’,monospace;
font-size:10px;letter-spacing:1px;
color:var(–c1);margin-top:6px;
}
.summary-saved-note.show{display:block;}

/* ─── CERTS SECTION ─── */
.certs-section{
margin-bottom:56px;
animation:fadeUp 0.6s 0.3s ease both;
}
.cert-grid{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(240px,1fr));
gap:12px;margin-top:24px;
}
.cert-card{
background:var(–card);border:1px solid var(–border);
border-radius:10px;padding:18px;
transition:border-color 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
}
.cert-card:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);border-color:var(–border2);}
.cc-top{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-start;gap:8px;margin-bottom:8px;}
.cc-name{
font-family:‘Syne’,sans-serif;
font-size:13px;font-weight:700;line-height:1.3;
}
.cc-badge{
font-family:‘JetBrains Mono’,monospace;
font-size:9px;padding:3px 7px;border-radius:3px;
white-space:nowrap;flex-shrink:0;
}
.free{background:rgba(79,255,176,0.08);color:var(–c1);border:1px solid rgba(79,255,176,0.15);}
.paid{background:rgba(255,209,102,0.08);color:var(–c3);border:1px solid rgba(255,209,102,0.15);}
.cc-provider{font-family:‘JetBrains Mono’,monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(–muted2);margin-bottom:6px;}
.cc-desc{font-size:12px;color:var(–muted2);font-weight:300;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:10px;}
.cc-timing{
font-family:‘JetBrains Mono’,monospace;font-size:10px;
padding:4px 10px;border-radius:4px;
display:inline-block;
}

/* ─── SECTION DIVIDER ─── */
.sec-divider{
display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;
margin-bottom:20px;
font-family:‘JetBrains Mono’,monospace;
font-size:9px;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;
color:var(–muted);
}
.sec-divider::after{content:’’;flex:1;height:1px;background:var(–border);}

/* ─── PROGRESS COMPLETE BANNER ─── */
.complete-banner{
display:none;
background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(79,255,176,0.08),rgba(79,195,247,0.08));
border:1px solid rgba(79,255,176,0.2);
border-radius:10px;padding:24px;
margin-bottom:48px;
text-align:center;
animation:popIn 0.4s cubic-bezier(.175,.885,.32,1.275) both;
}
.complete-banner.show{display:block;}
.complete-banner h3{
font-family:‘Syne’,sans-serif;font-size:20px;font-weight:800;
margin-bottom:8px;
background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(–c1),var(–c4));
-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;
background-clip:text;
}
.complete-banner p{font-size:13px;color:var(–muted2);font-weight:300;line-height:1.6;}

/* ─── PHASE COLORS ─── */
.phase-excel .ph-icon{background:rgba(79,195,247,0.1);}
.phase-excel .ph-title{color:var(–c4);}
.phase-excel .ph-weeks-badge{background:rgba(79,195,247,0.08);color:var(–c4);border:1px solid rgba(79,195,247,0.15);}
.phase-excel .wh-badge{background:rgba(79,195,247,0.08);color:var(–c4);}
.phase-excel .wh-prog-fill{background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(–c4),#74d7ff);}
.phase-excel .day-label{color:var(–c4);}
.phase-excel .summary-header{background:rgba(79,195,247,0.05);color:var(–c4);}
.phase-excel .summary-save-btn{background:var(–c4);color:#07080f;}
.phase-excel .cc-timing{background:rgba(79,195,247,0.08);color:var(–c4);}

.phase-powerbi .ph-icon{background:rgba(255,107,107,0.1);}
.phase-powerbi .ph-title{color:var(–c2);}
.phase-powerbi .ph-weeks-badge{background:rgba(255,107,107,0.08);color:var(–c2);border:1px solid rgba(255,107,107,0.15);}
.phase-powerbi .wh-badge{background:rgba(255,107,107,0.08);color:var(–c2);}
.phase-powerbi .wh-prog-fill{background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(–c2),#ff9a8b);}
.phase-powerbi .day-label{color:var(–c2);}
.phase-powerbi .summary-header{background:rgba(255,107,107,0.05);color:var(–c2);}
.phase-powerbi .summary-save-btn{background:var(–c2);color:#07080f;}
.phase-powerbi .cc-timing{background:rgba(255,107,107,0.08);color:var(–c2);}

.phase-ai .ph-icon{background:rgba(192,132,252,0.1);}
.phase-ai .ph-title{color:var(–c5);}
.phase-ai .ph-weeks-badge{background:rgba(192,132,252,0.08);color:var(–c5);border:1px solid rgba(192,132,252,0.15);}
.phase-ai .wh-badge{background:rgba(192,132,252,0.08);color:var(–c5);}
.phase-ai .wh-prog-fill{background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(–c5),#e0abff);}
.phase-ai .day-label{color:var(–c5);}
.phase-ai .summary-header{background:rgba(192,132,252,0.05);color:var(–c5);}
.phase-ai .summary-save-btn{background:var(–c5);color:#07080f;}
.phase-ai .cc-timing{background:rgba(192,132,252,0.08);color:var(–c5);}

.phase-final .ph-icon{background:rgba(255,209,102,0.1);}
.phase-final .ph-title{color:var(–c3);}
.phase-final .ph-weeks-badge{background:rgba(255,209,102,0.08);color:var(–c3);border:1px solid rgba(255,209,102,0.15);}
.phase-final .wh-badge{background:rgba(255,209,102,0.08);color:var(–c3);}
.phase-final .wh-prog-fill{background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(–c3),#ffe680);}
.phase-final .day-label{color:var(–c3);}
.phase-final .summary-header{background:rgba(255,209,102,0.05);color:var(–c3);}
.phase-final .summary-save-btn{background:var(–c3);color:#07080f;}
.phase-final .cc-timing{background:rgba(255,209,102,0.08);color:var(–c3);}

@keyframes fadeUp{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px);}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0);}}
@keyframes popIn{from{opacity:0;transform:scale(0.95);}to{opacity:1;transform:scale(1);}}

/* mobile */
@media(max-width:768px){
.sidebar{display:none;}
.main{padding:24px 16px 60px;}
}
</style>

</head>
<body>
<div class="app">

<!-- ═══ SIDEBAR ═══ -->

<aside class="sidebar">
  <div class="sidebar-logo">
    <div class="logo-tag">⚡ 8-Week Plan</div>
    <h2>Data & AI<br>Roadmap</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="sidebar-progress">
    <div class="sp-label">
      <span>Overall Progress</span>
      <span id="overall-pct">0%</span>
    </div>
    <div class="sp-bar-bg"><div class="sp-bar-fill" id="overall-bar" style="width:0%"></div></div>
    <div class="sp-count" id="overall-count">0 / 0 tasks</div>
  </div>
  <div id="sidebar-nav"></div>
</aside>

<!-- ═══ MAIN ═══ -->

<main class="main">

  <div class="hero">
    <div class="hero-eyebrow">// Your Personal Learning OS</div>
    <h1>Data & <em>AI Skills</em><br>Roadmap Tracker</h1>
    <p>Check off daily tasks, write your summaries (required), and track your journey to your first data job. Your progress saves automatically.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="stats-bar">
    <div class="stat-pill"><div class="pn">8</div><div class="pl">Weeks</div></div>
    <div class="stat-pill"><div class="pn">3</div><div class="pl">Skill Tracks</div></div>
    <div class="stat-pill"><div class="pn">6</div><div class="pl">Certs</div></div>
    <div class="stat-pill"><div class="pn">2–3h</div><div class="pl">Daily</div></div>
  </div>

  <div class="complete-banner" id="complete-banner">
    <h3>🎉 Roadmap Complete — You're Job-Ready!</h3>
    <p>You've completed all tasks and written every summary. Time to send those applications. You've built real skills, real projects, and real proof.</p>
  </div>

  <div id="phases-container"></div>

  <!-- CERTIFICATIONS -->

  <div class="certs-section">
    <div class="sec-divider">Certifications to Earn</div>
    <div class="cert-grid">
      <div class="cert-card phase-excel">
        <div class="cc-top"><div class="cc-name">MOS Excel Expert</div><div class="cc-badge paid">~$165</div></div>
        <div class="cc-provider">Microsoft / Certiport</div>
        <div class="cc-desc">Industry gold standard. Covers advanced formulas, Pivot Tables, macros. Recognised globally by employers.</div>
        <div class="cc-timing">⏱ Sit in Week 3–4</div>
      </div>
      <div class="cert-card phase-powerbi">
        <div class="cc-top"><div class="cc-name">PL-300: Power BI Analyst</div><div class="cc-badge paid">~$165</div></div>
        <div class="cc-provider">Microsoft Learn</div>
        <div class="cc-desc">Official Power BI cert. Highly valued in job postings. Free study materials on Microsoft Learn.</div>
        <div class="cc-timing">⏱ Sit in Week 5–6</div>
      </div>
      <div class="cert-card phase-excel">
        <div class="cc-top"><div class="cc-name">Google Data Analytics</div><div class="cc-badge paid">~$49/mo</div></div>
        <div class="cc-provider">Google / Coursera</div>
        <div class="cc-desc">Widely recognised. Covers data cleaning, visualisation, Sheets, SQL basics. Great for career changers.</div>
        <div class="cc-timing">⏱ Start Week 1 → Finish Week 6</div>
      </div>
      <div class="cert-card phase-ai">
        <div class="cc-top"><div class="cc-name">Prompt Engineering Cert</div><div class="cc-badge free">FREE</div></div>
        <div class="cc-provider">Vanderbilt / Coursera</div>
        <div class="cc-desc">Free audit. Covers prompt design, real use cases, AI ethics. ~6–8 hours total. Adds AI credibility.</div>
        <div class="cc-timing">⏱ Complete in Week 5</div>
