        <div class="cc-top"><div class="cc-name">AI for Everyone</div><div class="cc-badge free">FREE</div></div>
        <div class="cc-provider">Andrew Ng / DeepLearning.AI</div>
        <div class="cc-desc">Non-technical but high-value for analysts & ops roles. Teaches AI strategy and business impact. ~6 hours.</div>
        <div class="cc-timing">⏱ Complete in Week 5–6</div>
      </div>
      <div class="cert-card phase-excel">
        <div class="cc-top"><div class="cc-name">Excel Skills for Business</div><div class="cc-badge free">FREE Audit</div></div>
